<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Dashboard Admin ‚Äì RekaminAja</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
      tailwind.config = {
        theme: {
          extend: {
            fontFamily: {
              sans: ["Inter", "sans-serif"],
              mono: ["JetBrains Mono", "monospace"],
            },
          },
        },
      };
    </script>
  </head>

  <body
    class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-blue-500 selection:text-white"
  >
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <main class="pl-64 min-h-screen transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
      <header
        class="h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-8 border-b border-slate-800/50 bg-slate-950/50 backdrop-blur-sm sticky top-0 z-40"
      >
        <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2">
          üìä Dashboard Overview
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span
            class="text-xs text-green-400 bg-green-900/30 px-2 py-1 rounded-full border border-green-800 font-mono animate-pulse"
            >‚óè System Online</span
          >
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="p-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
            Selamat Datang, Admin.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mt-1">
            Berikut adalah status node dan sesi autentikasi Anda.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div
            class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-xl hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z"
                />
              </svg>
              Active Admin Address
            </h3>

            <div
              class="bg-slate-950/80 rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-800/80 shadow-inner flex items-center justify-between group"
            >
              <pre
                class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-sm break-all whitespace-pre-wrap"
              >
<%= admin %></pre
              >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-slate-400 transition-colors cursor-pointer ml-2 flex-shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M8 16H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v2m-6 12h8a2 2 0 002-2v-8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-8a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 flex items-center gap-1">
              <svg
                class="w-3 h-3"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"
                />
              </svg>
              Full Write Access to Smart Contract
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-xl hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all"
          >
            <h3
              class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                />
              </svg>
              Security Checks
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div
                  class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 mr-3 text-green-500"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                    />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Authenticated via Signature
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div
                  class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 mr-3 text-green-500"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                    />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Admin Verified On-Chain
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-300">
                <div
                  class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 mr-3 text-green-500"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
                    />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Secure Session Active
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-blue-950/40 border border-blue-800 rounded-lg p-4 flex items-center gap-4 shadow-sm"
        >
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 p-2 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-full">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="text-sm text-blue-200 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-100 block mb-1"
              >Security Notice</span
            >
            Pastikan untuk selalu melakukan logout jika mengakses dashboard dari
            perangkat publik. Private Key admin disimpan sementara di
            <code
              class="bg-blue-900/50 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-blue-300 text-xs font-mono"
              >localStorage</code
            >
            untuk penandatanganan transaksi.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
